热带风暴卡洛斯源于6月26日墨西哥以南的一股东风波。系统在逼近海岸线的过程中迅速强化，于6月27日以风速每小时100公里强度从[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]]上岸。风暴迅速退化成残留[[低氣壓|低气压区]]，并持续到6月29日才逐渐消散。<ref name="tcr">{{cite web | author = Miles B. Lawrence | date = 2003-08-04 | title = Tropical Storm Carlos Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-12-20 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003carlos.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131220010848/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003blanca.shtml | archivedate = 2013-12-20 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。墨西哥南部部分地区降下暴雨，[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]有两地的降雨量达到337毫米，是卡洛斯产生降水最多的所在<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/carlos2003.html | title = Tropical Storm Carlos Rainfall Summary | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130922040354/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/carlos2003.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-12-06 | archivedate = 2013-09-22 }}</ref>。风暴沿途导致约3万套房屋受损，经济损失约8670万[[墨西哥比索|比索]]（相当于2003年的800万美元）<ref>{{cite web | author = Sistema Nacional de Protección Civil: Centro Nacional de Prevención de Desastres | date = 2004-03 | title = Informe de la Temporada de Ciclones Tropicales del 2003 | publisher = El Secretario de Gobernación de Mexico | accessdate = 2014-12-06 | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141206154922/http://www.cenapred.unam.mx/es/Transparencia/FAQ/SISI/Anexo8.2/04_03_DI_RH_23032004.pdf | url = http://www.cenapred.unam.mx/es/Transparencia/FAQ/SISI/Anexo8.2/04_03_DI_RH_23032004.pdf | archivedate = 2014-12-06 }}</ref>。该国共有至少9人丧生，其中7人因[[泥石流|泥石流]]遇难，2人因河流泛滥而死，还有报道称两名渔夫失踪<ref name="ap627">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | date = 2003-06-23 | title = Tropical Storm Carlos dissipates after causing minor damage along Mexico's southern Pacific coast | agency = Associated Press}}</ref><ref name="dpa630">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | date = 2003-06-30 | title = Tropical Storm Carlos kills seven in Mexico | work = Deutsche Presse-Agentur}}</ref>。
